article_id:1570,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Remix Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599890400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6% from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The newly-added 5★ adventurer Incognito Nefaria (flame) and 5★ dragon Horus (flame) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragon:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Incognito Nefaria (flame/wand)</div><div>5★ Gala Elisanne (water/axe)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Horus (flame)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.80% (Adventurers: 1.00%, Dragons: 0.80%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 4.20% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 2.20%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%,　Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix active period:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599890400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1600149599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
